Package pt.ua.p2utils

Class BinarySearchTree<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • pt.ua.p2utils.BinarySearchTree<E>

  • public class BinarySearchTree<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    Binary search tree implementation of the dictionary ADT.

    This implementation does not guarantee a balanced tree. However, it should be reasonably balanced if keys are inserted randomly. Then, methods set, get, contains and remove should run in aproximately O(log n) time. The output of keys() is garanteed to be in lexicographical order, unlike that of HashTable.

    Author:
    Luís Seabra Lopes, João Manuel Rodrigues
